1
00:00:19,160 --> 00:00:20,520
You are pregnant.

2
00:00:20,540 --> 00:00:21,760
You can register at the clinic first

3
00:00:21,760 --> 00:00:23,410
and then start regular prenatal checkups.

4
00:00:23,410 --> 00:00:24,800
I'll prescribe some folic acid for you.

5
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:27,660
Pay on the first floor
and pick it up at the pharmacy.

6
00:00:42,510 --> 00:00:43,570
I want an abortion.

7
00:00:46,320 --> 00:00:47,390
For a termination,

8
00:00:47,390 --> 00:00:49,710
a family member has to be with you
and sign the consent.

9
00:00:49,710 --> 00:00:51,570
Do you want to think it over again?

10
00:00:53,320 --> 00:00:54,650
I don't have any family.

11
00:00:57,010 --> 00:01:00,380
[OB-GYN Clinic]

12
00:01:01,600 --> 00:01:02,970
Is there anyone else related to you?

13
00:01:02,970 --> 00:01:05,140
What do you mean by that?

14
00:01:05,590 --> 00:01:07,110
A partner or a friend.

15
00:01:08,070 --> 00:01:08,870
No.

16
00:01:10,030 --> 00:01:13,000
We cannot perform the procedure
without the consent and signature

17
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:15,060
of a family member or close relative.

18
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:16,480
We are a legitimate hospital.

19
00:01:16,480 --> 00:01:17,270
Everything has to be done by the book.

20
00:01:17,270 --> 00:01:20,000
[Restrooms on the Third Floor]

21
00:01:32,450 --> 00:01:34,250
Marry me, Xia Xue.

22
00:01:38,130 --> 00:01:40,570
Let me protect you for life.

23
00:03:26,410 --> 00:03:30,710
[THE GUILTY]

24
00:03:31,270 --> 00:03:35,410
[Episode 6]

25
00:03:40,980 --> 00:03:43,640
Mr. Ma, we've been following
Li Dong for a while.

26
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:44,680
After Ma Ke died,

27
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:46,150
he has been getting close to those people

28
00:03:46,150 --> 00:03:47,079
at the shipyard,

29
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:48,870
and he's been spending
more and more freely.

30
00:03:48,870 --> 00:03:50,220
Something feels fishy.

31
00:03:54,990 --> 00:03:57,250
I'll take you for a ride on my motorcycle.

32
00:03:57,630 --> 00:03:58,840
Can we go by car?

33
00:03:59,710 --> 00:04:01,120
A car? No problem.

34
00:04:01,630 --> 00:04:03,710
I'll give each of you a car.

35
00:04:03,710 --> 00:04:04,910
Really?

36
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:07,690
That depends on your performance.

37
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:09,160
-Okay.
-Okay.

38
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:10,600
Who is it?

39
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:11,730
What do you want?

40
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:28,480
Xue.

41
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:31,120
Xue.

42
00:04:36,640 --> 00:04:37,640
Xia Xue.

43
00:04:37,659 --> 00:04:38,460
Auntie.

44
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:41,600
Lu Ming told me you caught a cold.

45
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:42,920
I thought you might not feel like eating,

46
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:45,240
so I made some soup to help you recover.

47
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:46,600
Come in, please.

48
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:47,240
Okay.

49
00:04:50,950 --> 00:04:52,950
You're heading back to school soon,

50
00:04:53,110 --> 00:04:55,110
so you need to eat well and rest well.

51
00:04:56,430 --> 00:04:57,870
Here, drink the soup

52
00:04:57,870 --> 00:04:59,070
while it's still hot.

53
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:07,800
The first time I saw you,

54
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,740
you were only this big.

55
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:11,600
Your mother was holding you in her arms.

56
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:13,240
I liked you right away.

57
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:18,270
In the blink of an eye,

58
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:21,240
you and Lu Ming are both in college.

59
00:05:28,220 --> 00:05:29,150
Take this.

60
00:05:30,430 --> 00:05:31,240
Auntie.

61
00:05:31,400 --> 00:05:32,370
Listen to me.

62
00:05:33,270 --> 00:05:35,120
Though you're still young,

63
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:36,270
I've already decided that

64
00:05:36,270 --> 00:05:38,120
you'll be my daughter-in-law.

65
00:05:38,810 --> 00:05:40,730
This is a promise between us,

66
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:41,680
okay?

67
00:06:09,220 --> 00:06:11,660
[Loving Care Clinic, Painless Abortion]

68
00:06:12,310 --> 00:06:19,270
[Painless Abortion: Done in the Morning,
Back to Work in the Afternoon]

69
00:06:30,270 --> 00:06:32,690
Mr. Ma, we've caught Li Dong.

70
00:06:33,400 --> 00:06:34,800
We pressed him about Ma Ke's whereabouts

71
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:36,400
and got a few names out of him.

72
00:06:36,490 --> 00:06:39,070
They are all family members
of the shipyard workers.

73
00:06:39,070 --> 00:06:41,040
Then invite them over.

74
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:42,920
Yes, Mr. Ma.

75
00:06:53,260 --> 00:06:54,230
[Sancheng Financial Services]

76
00:06:54,230 --> 00:06:55,950
Rewrite it.

77
00:06:59,340 --> 00:07:02,840
[Ambition Through the Ages]

78
00:07:03,380 --> 00:07:04,260
Uncle San.

79
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:25,480
You are an interesting guy.

80
00:07:26,510 --> 00:07:27,870
This is the first time I've seen someone

81
00:07:27,870 --> 00:07:29,470
repay a loan shark like this.

82
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:31,540
Shouldn't I pay it back like this?

83
00:07:33,940 --> 00:07:35,990
If everyone were like you,

84
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:38,360
we'd have it way too easy.

85
00:07:40,820 --> 00:07:41,420
Uncle San.

86
00:07:42,430 --> 00:07:44,290
Can I discuss something with you?

87
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:44,920
Go ahead.

88
00:07:46,390 --> 00:07:48,050
I'm going back to school soon.

89
00:07:48,630 --> 00:07:50,360
Could you give me your account?

90
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:54,570
I'll earn the money doing part-time work
and transfer it to you.

91
00:07:58,140 --> 00:07:58,750
Chang.

92
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:01,060
How much does he still owe?

93
00:08:01,630 --> 00:08:03,080
About 170,000,

94
00:08:04,510 --> 00:08:05,710
excluding interest.

95
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:13,040
You can go.

96
00:08:13,270 --> 00:08:14,120
I'm not afraid you'll run.

97
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:14,680
[Harmony Above All]

98
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:16,790
I'll have Chang give you
the account later.

99
00:08:16,790 --> 00:08:17,990
Thank you, Uncle San.

100
00:08:18,830 --> 00:08:19,390
Wait.

101
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:24,850
You have a girlfriend

102
00:08:24,990 --> 00:08:26,220
named Xia Xue, right?

103
00:08:42,070 --> 00:08:43,530
Have you missed me lately?

104
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:45,030
You're so bad.

105
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:48,210
Is she new?

106
00:08:48,360 --> 00:08:49,690
What are you looking at?

107
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:00,960
What did they say?

108
00:09:03,270 --> 00:09:05,800
They know about
my relationship with Xia Xue.

109
00:09:06,390 --> 00:09:07,920
Let's go buy tickets first.

110
00:09:08,280 --> 00:09:10,280
Go pack your things and come with us.

111
00:09:10,800 --> 00:09:11,440
Me?

112
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:13,670
Where would I go?

113
00:09:13,840 --> 00:09:14,910
Come with us.

114
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:17,840
I can't leave.

115
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:20,040
Li Dong is under control for now,

116
00:09:20,390 --> 00:09:23,360
but if he can ask for money once,
he can do it again.

117
00:09:23,870 --> 00:09:24,550
And he might

118
00:09:24,550 --> 00:09:26,010
tell Ma Derong about this.

119
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:29,360
If I leave,

120
00:09:29,550 --> 00:09:30,720
