121
00:09:33,280 --> 00:09:34,830
He won't do anything to me.

122
00:09:34,850 --> 00:09:35,870
He just wants money.

123
00:09:35,870 --> 00:09:37,870
Even if he kills me, I don't have any.

124
00:09:39,390 --> 00:09:40,550
Don't worry about me.

125
00:09:40,550 --> 00:09:41,750
Let's go buy tickets.

126
00:09:41,880 --> 00:09:42,410
Let's go.

127
00:09:44,450 --> 00:09:46,070
[Nanping Station]

128
00:09:46,070 --> 00:09:46,870
Excuse me.

129
00:09:46,870 --> 00:09:47,990
Sorry. Excuse me.

130
00:09:48,120 --> 00:09:48,790
I'm in a real hurry.

131
00:09:48,790 --> 00:09:49,900
Excuse me.

132
00:09:49,920 --> 00:09:50,410
Hello.

133
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:52,120
Two tickets to Huacheng, please.

134
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:52,920
For which day?

135
00:09:53,050 --> 00:09:54,150
The sooner, the better.

136
00:09:54,150 --> 00:09:56,510
The earliest tickets to Huacheng
are for the day after tomorrow.

137
00:09:56,510 --> 00:09:57,270
Any earlier ones?

138
00:09:57,270 --> 00:09:58,800
Standing tickets are fine.

139
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:00,700
There's nothing earlier.

140
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:02,790
Are you two buying tickets or not?

141
00:10:02,790 --> 00:10:03,630
Are you buying tickets or not?

142
00:10:03,630 --> 00:10:04,750
If not, step aside.

143
00:10:04,750 --> 00:10:05,390
We're in a hurry.

144
00:10:05,390 --> 00:10:05,910
Sorry.

145
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:07,630
Students are returning to school recently,

146
00:10:07,630 --> 00:10:09,150
