147
00:10:09,150 --> 00:10:10,330
It's risky to wait.

148
00:10:10,470 --> 00:10:12,270
Let's check the refund counter.

149
00:10:12,790 --> 00:10:13,360
Okay.

150
00:10:15,150 --> 00:10:16,120
It's packed over there for food.

151
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:16,720
You even have to wait for a table.

152
00:10:16,720 --> 00:10:17,480
[Prevent Disease, Maintain Hygiene]

153
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:18,810
If you don't go early...

154
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:24,270
What's wrong, miss?

155
00:10:24,270 --> 00:10:25,670
Are you not feeling well?

156
00:10:26,750 --> 00:10:27,480
Come here.

157
00:10:28,870 --> 00:10:29,600
Come here.

158
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:43,720
How could you be so careless?

159
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:46,120
How much?

160
00:10:46,390 --> 00:10:47,120
600.

161
00:10:48,150 --> 00:10:48,720
Cheng.

162
00:10:49,120 --> 00:10:50,080
Take her inside.

163
00:10:52,510 --> 00:10:55,250
How long until I recover after it's done?

164
00:10:55,390 --> 00:10:56,550
Isn't it obvious?

165
00:10:56,550 --> 00:10:59,320
Done in the morning, you can
be back at work in the afternoon.

166
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:00,510
It's just an abortion.

167
00:11:00,510 --> 00:11:02,150
It's not like sawing off a leg.

168
00:11:02,150 --> 00:11:02,880
Go on inside.

169
00:11:10,270 --> 00:11:10,870
Sit there.

170
00:11:13,620 --> 00:11:19,910
[Ward Safety Management Regulations]

171
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:26,200
Little one.

172
00:11:27,510 --> 00:11:28,600
Don't be nervous.

173
00:11:28,670 --> 00:11:29,720
It's just

174
00:11:29,790 --> 00:11:31,120
a small procedure.

175
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:33,600
I do plenty of these every year.

176
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:36,720
Don't worry.

177
00:11:37,050 --> 00:11:38,380
It'll be over in no time.

178
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:42,120
Where is she?

179
00:11:57,620 --> 00:11:59,390
Hello, are you here to
return tickets to Huacheng?

180
00:11:59,390 --> 00:11:59,910
Hello.

181
00:11:59,910 --> 00:12:01,840
Is anyone returning tickets to Huacheng?

182
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:03,390
No, no, no.

183
00:12:04,270 --> 00:12:06,470
Are you returning tickets to Huacheng?

184
00:12:07,030 --> 00:12:08,490
You want to go to Huacheng?

185
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:09,840
Yes.

186
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:10,750
How many tickets?

187
00:12:10,750 --> 00:12:11,550
For which day?

188
00:12:11,840 --> 00:12:12,840
Two for tomorrow.

189
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:45,590
Sir, drive!

190
00:12:54,090 --> 00:12:55,780
Xia Xue, where did you go?

191
00:12:56,150 --> 00:12:57,880
We looked for you all this time.

192
00:12:58,360 --> 00:12:59,560
I was being followed.

193
00:12:59,720 --> 00:13:01,450
Where were they following you?

194
00:13:01,910 --> 00:13:02,910
Xiaohai Village.

195
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:06,520
What were you doing in Xiaohai Village?

196
00:13:07,300 --> 00:13:08,960
I just went to buy some things.

197
00:13:10,240 --> 00:13:11,600
Have we been exposed?

198
00:13:14,440 --> 00:13:15,440
Could it be

199
00:13:17,960 --> 00:13:19,120
Ma Derong?

200
00:13:24,080 --> 00:13:25,600
How would he know?

201
00:13:29,320 --> 00:13:30,380
No matter who it is,

202
00:13:31,630 --> 00:13:33,030
we can't wait any longer.

203
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:35,030
We must leave here immediately.

204
00:13:35,030 --> 00:13:35,560
Let's go.

205
00:13:36,200 --> 00:13:36,960
They...

206
00:13:43,120 --> 00:13:45,120
Lin Hua, are you coming with us?

207
00:13:45,120 --> 00:13:46,120
You two go first.

208
00:13:46,120 --> 00:13:47,270
I'll come find you once I've taken care of

209
00:13:47,270 --> 00:13:48,200
the mess at home.

210
00:13:50,720 --> 00:13:51,360
Hurry.

211
00:13:53,610 --> 00:13:54,610
Let's go.

212
00:13:55,120 --> 00:13:55,860
Dear passengers, please pay attention.

213
00:13:55,860 --> 00:13:57,000
[Ticket Hall]

214
00:13:57,000 --> 00:13:58,240
Please take care of

215
00:13:58,240 --> 00:14:00,480
your personal belongings and valuables

216
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:02,220
to prevent loss or theft.

217
00:14:02,220 --> 00:14:02,630
[Luggage Storage]

218
00:14:02,630 --> 00:14:05,120
It is strictly forbidden to carry
flammable, explosive, toxic,

219
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:07,080
and other dangerous items
into the station or onto the train.

220
00:14:07,080 --> 00:14:09,570
Any violations will be dealt
with according to the law.

221
00:14:09,570 --> 00:14:11,270
To ensure the safety of the journey...

222
00:14:11,270 --> 00:14:12,120
I'll distract them.

223
00:14:12,120 --> 00:14:13,080
You two get on first.

224
00:14:13,080 --> 00:14:14,120
If we leave, we leave together.

225
00:14:14,120 --> 00:14:14,720
There are police everywhere.

226
00:14:14,720 --> 00:14:15,600
They won't do anything.

227
00:14:15,600 --> 00:14:16,360
We can't make a scene.

228
00:14:16,360 --> 00:14:17,630
If the police notice us…

229
00:14:17,630 --> 00:14:18,240
Lin Hua!

230
00:14:23,600 --> 00:14:24,360
Who are you?

231
00:14:24,480 --> 00:14:25,540
Why did you trip me?

232
00:14:25,600 --> 00:14:27,030
Everyone, look!

233
00:14:28,120 --> 00:14:29,550
If you didn't trip me, how did I fall?

234
00:14:29,550 --> 00:14:30,510
Why did you trip me?

235
00:14:30,510 --> 00:14:31,600
Who tripped you?

236
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:34,130
If you didn't trip me,
how did I fall? Officer!

237
00:14:34,960 --> 00:14:36,320
They tripped me!

238
00:14:36,320 --> 00:14:37,600
They're bullying a disabled person!

239
00:14:37,600 --> 00:14:39,400
Stop making a fuss. One at a time.

240
00:14:39,460 --> 00:14:39,960
[Waiting Area for
Huacheng-Bound Passengers]

241
00:14:39,960 --> 00:14:41,320
Passengers going to Huacheng,

242
00:14:41,320 --> 00:14:41,910
please line up.

243
00:14:41,910 --> 00:14:44,670
Passengers traveling to Huacheng,
please line up for ticket check.

244
00:14:44,670 --> 00:14:45,550
Alright, you're in Car Three..

245
00:14:45,550 --> 00:14:46,390
Passengers traveling to Huacheng,...

246
00:14:46,390 --> 00:14:48,590
Is there anyone else going to Huacheng?

247
00:14:49,360 --> 00:14:50,120
Excuse me.

248
00:14:50,480 --> 00:14:51,390
We are college students.

249
00:14:51,390 --> 00:14:52,600
We must get back to school today,

250
00:14:52,600 --> 00:14:53,870
but our tickets are for tomorrow.

251
00:14:53,870 --> 00:14:55,870
Could you please make an exception?

252
00:14:56,510 --> 00:14:57,720
No way. No way.

253
00:14:57,720 --> 00:14:58,550
Why?

254
00:14:59,000 --> 00:15:00,750
Your tickets are fake.

255
00:15:00,750 --> 00:15:01,630
They're fake.

256
00:15:03,480 --> 00:15:05,210
Is there anyone else going to Huacheng?

257
00:15:05,210 --> 00:15:06,240
Anyone else?

258
00:15:06,240 --> 00:15:06,840
Lu Ming.

259
00:15:08,390 --> 00:15:09,200
Xia Xue.

260
00:15:09,890 --> 00:15:11,450
Mr. Ma wants to see you two.

261
00:15:11,550 --> 00:15:12,750
Come with me.

262
00:15:14,390 --> 00:15:15,430
[Waiting Area for
Chengdu-Bound Passengers]

263
00:15:15,430 --> 00:15:17,030
You two know very well

264
00:15:17,030 --> 00:15:18,760
what dirty things you've done.

265
00:15:19,240 --> 00:15:21,300
So don't trouble the police anymore.

266
00:15:37,380 --> 00:15:38,630
Uncle.

267
00:15:48,480 --> 00:15:49,720
Uncle.

268
00:16:07,630 --> 00:16:09,120
Ma Ke's death

269
00:16:09,440 --> 00:16:12,720
really had nothing to do with me.

270
00:16:19,480 --> 00:16:22,840
It was Lu Ming, Lin Hua, and Xia Xue.

271
00:16:23,080 --> 00:16:25,720
They killed him.

272
00:16:34,190 --> 00:16:35,970
What else? Say it!

273
00:16:36,960 --> 00:16:37,600
Say it!

274
00:16:40,720 --> 00:16:41,480
Uncle.

275
00:16:42,750 --> 00:16:44,480
Spare me.

276
00:16:45,480 --> 00:16:48,600
I just wanted to extort
some money from Lu Ming.

277
00:16:50,200 --> 00:16:51,700
I was going to hand

278
00:16:51,970 --> 00:16:54,790
the backup tape over to you anyway.

279
00:16:54,960 --> 00:16:57,240
I was wrong, Uncle.

280
00:17:01,510 --> 00:17:02,720
Ma Ke and I

281
00:17:02,960 --> 00:17:05,550
grew up together, Uncle.

282
00:17:06,430 --> 00:17:08,690
Please spare me.

283
00:17:09,200 --> 00:17:10,829
Just 200,000.

284
00:17:15,109 --> 00:17:15,589
Uncle.

285
00:17:16,829 --> 00:17:18,750
I really don't dare anymore.

